    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-12-10T03:35:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-12-10T03:35:00-05:00" n="512"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d512">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.24591/22: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tehran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-12-10T12:00:00+03:25"
                            >December 10, 1943—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received December 10—10:50
                        a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1103. Iranian Government has interposed last minute objections to proposed
                    agreement covering American troops in Iran. Department’s telegram No. 612,
                    December 2, 4 p.m. and extensive previous correspondence. Foreign Minister
                    advised me that changes now desired are being transmitted to his Minister at
                    Washington, and has handed me copy of his covering instructions which indicate
                    that no possibility exists of any immediate conclusion of agreement. Report
                    covering present status of discussions is being forwarded by air.</p>
                <p>In view of these circumstances I now propose to depart on my deferred home leave
                    by next ATC<note n="73" xml:id="d512fn73">Air Transport Command.</note>
                    plane.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
